23 class MeetupServiceImpl @Inject()(protected val dbConfigProvider: DatabaseConfigProvider,
24                            applicationConfig: ApplicationConfig,

28     extends MeetupService {
29 
30   val log = Logger("service.meetup")
31 
32   val format = new SimpleDateFormat("yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss")
33 
34   def getEventData(group: String, id: String): Future[Option[Model.Event]] = {
35     val request = ws.url(config.url + group + "/events/" + id)
36       .addQueryStringParameters("key" -> config.apiKey, "fields" -> "time,photo_album")
37       
38     val result = request.get()
39 
40     result.map { case x =>
41       log.debug("Got response from meetup api: " + x.body)
42       val res = x.json.validate[Model.Event]
43       log.debug(res.toString())
44       res.asOpt
45     }
46   }
47 
48   def getEvent(url: String, login: Login): Future[Option[EventDetail]] = {
49     val t = new URI(url).getPath.split("/")
50     val i = t.indexOf("events")
51     getEventData(t(i-1),t(i+1)).map(_.map(x => toEventDetail(x)))
52   }
53 
54   def canImport(url: String, login: Login) = {
55     val uri = new URI(url)
56     val split = uri.getPath.split("/").indexOf("events")
57     (uri.getHost.equals("www.meetup.com") || uri.getHost.equals("www.meetup.de")) && split >= 0
58   }
59 
60   def toEventDetail(data: Model.Event): EventDetail = {
61     val loc = Location(None, data.venue.name, Some(data.venue.lat), Some(data.venue.lon),
62                             data.venue.country, data.venue.city, data.venue.street.getOrElse(data.venue.address_1.getOrElse("")), None,
63                             data.venue.phone, None, None, data.venue.zip)
64 
65     val from = new Timestamp(data.time)
66 
67     EventDetail(None, data.name, from,
68                 None, data.plain_text_no_images_description.orElse(data.plain_text_description).getOrElse(data.description), "",
69                 Organizer(None,"Organizer",-1,None), List(/*TODO Categories*/),
70                 None, loc,
71                 data.photo_album.map(_.photo_sample).getOrElse(List()).map(x => TaggedImage(None,None,None,Some(x.photo_link))), 0,
72                 None, None) //TODO Prices
73   }
74 }
